replies.body:
I remember I had a discussion with you at the end of season 4 where I gave reasons why this team composition is sub-optimal. Main reasons were map pressure, trading, and the fact that the team composition is 80% AP (especially top half of the map). I would say that in the current meta this team composition would get stomped even quicker than back in those times.
Its like going to war with the same strategy every time, despite what the enemies do... doomed to fail.

But the problem that you currently face is players taking orders... nobody likes that. If you can't convince players that this strategy will work, then its not gonna happen. Perhaps if you offered some incentives to some bronze-silver-golds to play this in flex queue they could try it out {{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}}
